<ttl id="1002J_S0010_72VAG_T004O" variety="T004O">
<name>STEERING ANGLE SENSOR (w/ VSC)</name>
<para id="RM000000SS7007X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="BC054-07" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000000SS7007X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000000SS7007X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00000LA00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT STEERING ANGLE SENSOR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Inspect the steering angle sensor. If any of the following occurs, replace the steering angle sensor with a new one:</ptxt>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>The surface of the steering angle sensor is cracked, dented, or chipped off.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>The connector is scratched, cracked, or damaged.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>The steering angle sensor has been dropped.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
